Are you backing the Parliamentary pick Rishi Sunak with his plan to tackle rising inflation and promises of Thatcherite reforms? Or have you been swayed by grassroots favourite Liz Truss’s bold pledge for immediate tax cuts and a return to Conservative values? Are you impressed by the former Chancellor’s smooth TV performances, or do you prefer the Foreign Secretary’s tough talking? Tell us in around 150 words who you want to see in No 10 and why. If you email newpm@reachplc.com you may find your views printed in the newspaper.